headline: Dell Technologies price target raised to $154 from $136 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley raised the firm’s price target on Dell Technologies (DELL) to $154 from $136 and keeps an Overweight rating on the shares. AI server momentum “remains strong,” says the analyst, who notes that the firm’s recent checks point to about $20B of AI server revenue in FY26, which is 56% higher than the firm’s prior forecast.
